ttp://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Track & field action begins tomorrow starting live at 4:05 a.m.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Track & field\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ET on E!\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"with preliminary heats and later at 1 p.m.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET on NBC and Peacock, headlined by the lone final of the day in the men's 10,000m.\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999961838402724, \"rank\": 3.813277764637362e-06, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1842, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999996279244224, \"rank\": 3.7207470948009664e-07, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickherefor more information on tomorrow's coverage.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"***  Following are highlights from today's coverage of the Paris Olympics on the platforms of NBCUniversal:  GYMNASTICS  Laurie Hernandez before Biles' floor routine, clinching the women's all-around gold medal: \\\"Everything has led to this moment for her.\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2088, \"end\": 2104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurie Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All her wins, all her losses, and all the greatness that she has in her.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's come to this.\\\"\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rich Lerner on Biles' floor routine: \\\"That's what greatness looks like.\\\"\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hernandez on Biles' vault: \\\"You will not see anyone get as high as she does.\\\"\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lerner on Simone Biles' opening score of 15.766 in vault: \\\"That's her standard.\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She does gymnastics that no one else does or has done.\\\"\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lerner on the competitiveness of Suni Lee, who won bronze in the all-around: \\\"The word you typically hear to describe Lee is 'gamer.'\\\"\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2640, \"end\": 2648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suni Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2725, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9998597275641286, \"rank\": 0.00014003997462772732, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hernandez: \\\"She is absolutely a gamer.\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She may have a few mistakes in warmups, yet when the pressure is on, she's able to get her routines together.\\\"\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2892, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lerner on the talent of the U.S. women's gymnastics team: \\\"(The U.S. men's basketball) team has\\u2026an embarrassment of riches - the same could be said of Team USA women's gymnastics with the two Olympic all-around champions in Simone Biles and Suni Lee.\\\"\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2958, \"end\": 2962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999182788616587, \"rank\": 5.819066086171509e-05, \"text\": \"U.S.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3045, \"end\": 3053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9180920558990361, \"rank\": 0.08921499233912697, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3135, \"end\": 3143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suni Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lerner on Algeria's Kaylia Nemour: \\\"Whatever happens, medal or no medal, she has announced herself as a gymnast to watch in the coming years.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3157, \"end\": 3164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6381863902476425, \"rank\": 0.5669403402815969, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just 17 [years old].\\\"\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SWIMMING  Rowdy Gaines on Kate Douglass winning her first Olympic gold medal in the women's 200m breaststroke: \\\"Nobody in the world is better on that pullout than Kate Douglass\\u2026Oui, oui, you are an Olympic medalist!\\\"\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3322, \"end\": 3334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rowdy Gaines\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rowdy_Gaines\"}, {\"begin\": 3338, \"end\": 3351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kate Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\"}, {\"begin\": 3475, \"end\": 3488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kate Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\"}, {\"begin\": 3489, \"end\": 3492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oui_(magazine)\", \"score\": 0.9856235650398876, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oui\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oui_(magazine)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oui_(magazine)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaines on Leon Marchand in the men's 200m IM semifinal: \\\"Does he have a weak stroke?\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, that's relative\\u2026Look at his face.\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His face is not tight at all, it's relaxed.\", \"from\": 3655, \"to\": 3698, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's almost like he's gazing up to the stars on a beautiful Paris summer night.\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3759, \"end\": 3764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7958161923273185e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's how good it looks.\\\"\", \"from\": 3779, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dan Hicks on Marchand: \\\"Through all this chaotic atmosphere and 15,000-plus cheering his every move and every stroke, Marchand continues to be the calmest guy in La Defense Arena.\\\"\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gaines on his conversation with Marchand after winning two gold medals on Wednesday: \\\"I said to him, 'Hey, great job yesterday.\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4021, \"end\": 4029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.999999994935024, \"rank\": 4.7814469511668e-09, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"America was electrified.'\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said, 'Really?\", \"from\": 4143, \"to\": 4160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's so exciting!'\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was just a real humble guy.\\\"\", \"from\": 4182, \"to\": 4213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GOLF  France's Victor Perez to Rex Hoggard on hitting the opening tee shot in his home country: \\\"It's a once in a lifetime opportunity for me.\", \"from\": 4215, \"to\": 4357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4221, \"end\": 4227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9918050450360719, \"rank\": 0.0052254055658180485, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4230, \"end\": 4242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Perez\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.2148334013930144e-13, \"text\": \"Victor Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Perez\"}, {\"begin\": 4246, \"end\": 4249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rex_Britten\", \"score\": 0.9999999998826752, \"rank\": 1.1752126932856374e-10, \"text\": \"Rex\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rex_Britten\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rex_Britten\"}, {\"begin\": 4250, \"end\": 4257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hoggard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hoggard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hoggard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Hoggard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will never be able to hit this shot, this exact shot, opening the Olympics at home, ever again.\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just wanted to soak it all in.\\\"\", \"from\": 4456, \"to\": 4489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael Phelps on the atmosphere of the Paris Games at Le Golf National: \\\"Being back to a real Games\\u2026being able to have the fanbase from all over the world back here\\u2026you can feel the energy, you can feel the electricity\\u2026The Olympics is about bringing people together.\\\"\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4491, \"end\": 4505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.014482763864082e-65, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TENNIS  Mary Carillo on China's Qinwen Zheng upsetting world No.\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4769, \"end\": 4781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Carillo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mary Carillo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Carillo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Carillo\"}, {\"begin\": 4785, \"end\": 4790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9512619659060977, \"rank\": 0.05121687077863349, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 4800, \"end\": 4805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999999984174792, \"rank\": 1.4239752328655738e-09, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1 Iga Swiatek to advance to the gold medal match: \\\"You have got to give her all kinds of props.\", \"from\": 4826, \"to\": 4921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She beat a woman who, on this surface, on this particular court, has had such an uncomplicated superiority for so long.\", \"from\": 4922, \"to\": 5041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's Qinwen Zheng with a win of her life, at the most important tournament for China.\\\"\", \"from\": 5042, \"to\": 5132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5058, \"end\": 5063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999999984174792, \"rank\": 1.4239752328655738e-09, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}, {\"begin\": 5125, \"end\": 5130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9512619659060977, \"rank\": 0.05121687077863349, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WOMEN'S BASKETBALL  LaChina Robinson on Britney Griner's elite interior defense: \\\"There are two scenarios that are very similar.\", \"from\": 5134, \"to\": 5262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5182, \"end\": 5188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Griner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not want to try to take a charge onLeBron(James), and I do not know if you want to go to the rim against Britney Griner.\\\"\", \"from\": 5263, \"to\": 5391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5383, \"end\": 5389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Griner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Noah Eagle on Breanna Stewart and A'ja Wilson: \\\"They are the definition of modern basketball, to a T. Length, skill, inside, outside, all three levels.\\\"\", \"from\": 5393, \"to\": 5545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5407, \"end\": 5422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Breanna Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\"}, {\"begin\": 5427, \"end\": 5438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"A'ja Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MEN'S BASKETBALL  Snoop Dogg on his experience riding with Team USA men's basketball team to yesterday's game, a win vs. South Sudan:\\\"I felt a lot of brotherhood, camaraderie.\", \"from\": 5547, \"to\": 5722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5606, \"end\": 5614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9180920558990361, \"rank\": 0.08921499233912697, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5668, \"end\": 5679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9982583984803384, \"rank\": 0.0017435401873037318, \"text\": \"South Sudan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt them ego-checking themselves at the door\\u2026I see that there is really no animosity amongst the players as far as they all love and support each other\\u2026They know that this team was put together reminiscent of the Dream Team in the spirit of having the best of the best represent the country.\", \"from\": 5723, \"to\": 6017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5939, \"end\": 5949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999630385907, \"rank\": 3.696129159199147e-08, \"text\": \"Dream Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not about me, it's about we, and we have got to put our best foot forward to perform at a high level.\", \"from\": 6018, \"to\": 6124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that these players understand that.\", \"from\": 6125, \"to\": 6168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why they have been selected\\u2026They know that this is the biggest thing, bigger than the world championship.\\\"\", \"from\": 6169, \"to\": 6282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"***  ABOUT NBC OLYMPICS  The NBC broadcast network and streaming service Peacock are the company's primary platforms for its coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 6284, \"to\": 6450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6313, \"end\": 6316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999961838402724, \"rank\": 3.813277764637362e-06, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCU owns the U.S. media rights to the Olympic Games through 2032, which are scheduled for Paris (2024), Milan Cortina (2026), Los Angeles (2028) and Brisbane (2032).\", \"from\": 6451, \"to\": 6617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6451, \"end\": 6455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/